cool_faces
==========

about
-----

=> generate cool ASCII slash Unicode faces <=

( ͡° ͜ʖ ͡°)

This crate is derived from [`cool-ascii-faces`](https://www.npmjs.com/package/cool-ascii-faces)
from Max Odgen and contributors.

`faces` has a few extra features. You can ask for happy, angry, sad or meh faces
with the appropriate functions:

usage
-----

    cool_faces::angry() -> "(ಠ_ಠ)" | "(╯°□°）╯︵ ┻━┻" | ...
    cool_faces::confused() -> "٩◔̯◔۶" | ...
    cool_faces::disappointed() -> "¬_¬" | ...
    cool_faces::excited() -> "ᕕ( ᐛ )ᕗ" | ...
    cool_faces::happy() -> "=^.^=" | ...
    cool_faces::meh() -> "¯\\_(ツ)_/¯" | ...
    cool_faces::sad() -> "༼ ºل͟º ༽" | ...
    cool_faces::deal_with_it() -> "(⌐■_■)"


